	<h3>Store Configuration</h3>
	<p>Each FloodBoy store monitors:</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Battery voltage (V x100)</li>
		<li>Installation height (m x10000)</li>
		<li>Water depth (m x10000)</li>
		<li>Min/Max values for trend analysis</li>
		<li>Sample counts for data quality</li>
	</ul>

