	<p>FloodBoy has been successfully deployed across Northern Thailand, including:</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Don Chan area flood monitoring points</li>
		<li>Sri Ping Mueang community</li>
		<li>Mae On District risk areas</li>
		<li>Mae Fah Luang University dormitory areas</li>
	</ul>
	
